jProtocol.Abstract.View.keyvaluetree

Class KeyValueObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • jProtocol.Abstract.View.keyvaluetree.KeyValueObject

  • public class KeyValueObject
extends java.lang.Object
    A KeyValueObject has a key, an optional value and optional children and can be displayed in a KeyValueTree. A background color and a HTML info text can be set additionally.
    Author:
    Tom Petersen, 2015
